Gold Price in Hong Kong Up
HONG KONG , September 21 ( Xinhua ) -- The gold price in Hong Kong rose 6 HK dollars to close at 2,668 HK dollars a tael on Monday , according to Po Sang Bank , one of the major gold dealers in Hong Kong .
The gold price is equivalent to 289.08 U.S. dollars a troy ounce , up 0.66 U.S. dollar from the previous close at Monday 's exchange rate of one U.S. dollar to 7.7473 HK dollars .
